Walk Like a Panther is a 2018 British comedy film directed by Dan Cadan and starring Stephen Graham, Jason Flemyng, Julian Sands, Jill Halfpenny, Robbie Gee, Stephen Tompkinson and Sue Johnston.[1][2] Filming took place in Marsden, a large village in West Yorkshire.

A group of 1980s wrestlers are forced to don the lycra one last time when their beloved local pub, The Half Nelson, is threatened with closure.

On 8 March 2018, Rick Astley released a song and music video for Walk like a Panther.[3]

The film holds an 8% approval rating at Rotten Tomatoes.[4]
